    "long_instructions": "### Loop a Backbeat for 24 Measures\r\n\r\nMaria is making a song that lasts for 24 measures. She has enough lyrics to fill her song, but she needs a catchy backbeat. Create a combination of sounds that uses at least one beat, one bass, and one effect. Code it in a way that will make that loop last for 24 measures. ",
